WEBVTT

01:50.520 --> 01:53.280
Fine, then I should thank you.

01:53.720 --> 01:55.280
Thank you, Meng.

01:56.000 --> 01:57.000
You're welcome.

02:30.680 --> 02:31.280
By the way,

02:31.800 --> 02:33.320
in my spare time,

02:33.520 --> 02:35.640
I've been selling insurance for over ten years.

02:35.640 --> 02:38.840
Time was too tight at the parent-teacher meeting that day.

02:38.840 --> 02:41.440
I didn't get to explain it to your mom carefully.

02:41.440 --> 02:44.300
I recommend they buy a critical illness insurance.

02:44.480 --> 02:46.680
This insurance is very beneficial.

02:46.880 --> 02:48.160
When you go to college,

02:48.200 --> 02:49.760
you'll be far away and won't be able to look after them.

02:49.760 --> 02:52.820
With this insurance, everyone will have peace of mind.

02:53.120 --> 02:53.720
By the way,

02:54.320 --> 02:56.000
I have two contracts here.

02:56.160 --> 02:57.960
Take them home for your parents to look at.

02:57.960 --> 03:00.640
If they have any questions, they can ask me anytime,

03:00.640 --> 03:01.280
okay?

03:01.520 --> 03:03.240
Auntie, you're right.

03:03.760 --> 03:05.420
I'll find time to talk to them.

03:07.440 --> 03:08.160
Great.

03:08.240 --> 03:10.160
Look how sensible he is.

03:10.360 --> 03:11.640
Come, let's eat.

03:11.680 --> 03:12.520
No contract today.

03:12.520 --> 03:13.120
Let's just eat.

03:13.120 --> 03:14.120
Take it with you when you leave.

03:14.120 --> 03:15.200
Jingu, eat more.

03:15.960 --> 03:16.920
Have some more.

03:20.040 --> 03:20.760
Let's eat.

03:30.320 --> 03:31.480
Well, deskmate.

03:31.720 --> 03:33.440
About what my mom said today,

03:33.920 --> 03:35.200
she was just saying it casually.

03:35.200 --> 03:36.360
Don't take it to heart.

03:36.360 --> 03:38.520
Can I come over at 1:00 PM on Saturday?

03:40.480 --> 03:42.400
I think so.

03:43.360 --> 03:44.920
It's fine if you don't come.

03:45.120 --> 03:46.400
Don't come. It's okay.

03:47.840 --> 03:48.600
Yuanbao,

03:49.400 --> 03:50.240
I know

03:50.920 --> 03:53.360
you are still mad at me about what happened that day.

03:53.360 --> 03:55.320
I wanted to explain it to you afterwards,

03:55.320 --> 03:56.600
but the situation was a bit complicated.

03:56.600 --> 03:58.200
I didn't know how to tell you,

03:58.520 --> 04:00.650
so I didn't contact you for a long time.

04:00.800 --> 04:02.160
But Yuanbao, please believe me.

04:02.160 --> 04:03.090
I had my reasons.

04:03.400 --> 04:04.800
I didn't do it on purpose.

04:05.000 --> 04:05.680
So,

04:06.520 --> 04:08.720
please don't be mad at me anymore, okay?

04:08.720 --> 04:10.520
I understand.

04:11.480 --> 04:14.810
It's just that everyone was a bit disappointed at that time.

04:17.040 --> 04:19.300
I'll come over for tutoring on Saturday.

04:23.840 --> 04:25.520
See you on Saturday then.

04:26.080 --> 04:28.000
Thank you for the trouble.

04:28.200 --> 04:29.860
No trouble at all. I'd love to.

04:31.920 --> 04:33.200
Since your mom said so,

04:33.360 --> 04:35.360
don't forget to join us on Saturday.

04:36.320 --> 04:39.000
Sure. I want to see how you teach.

04:39.600 --> 04:42.000
Then you can teach if I get something wrong.

04:42.840 --> 04:43.800
I wouldn't dare.

04:44.120 --> 04:45.880
You are so good at studying.

04:48.440 --> 04:51.080
What's wrong with you two?

04:52.840 --> 04:53.480
Yuanbao,

04:54.120 --> 04:56.280
get some rest. I'll go back now.

04:56.640 --> 04:57.400
See you on Saturday.

04:57.400 --> 04:58.040
Bye.

05:07.160 --> 05:08.890
Did you step on my foot just now?

05:09.920 --> 05:11.600
Not me.

05:12.320 --> 05:13.240
It was you.

05:13.560 --> 05:14.360
Don't run.

05:14.600 --> 05:16.360
You stepped on my foot. Why did you do that?

05:16.360 --> 05:17.480
Stop right there.

05:20.320 --> 05:21.920
If you were like this before,

05:22.280 --> 05:24.160
wouldn't your grades have improved long ago?

05:24.160 --> 05:26.720
And you wouldn't score worse than me every time.

05:26.720 --> 05:28.480
You're obviously a physics genius.

05:28.480 --> 05:29.360
Why do you pretend to know nothing

05:29.360 --> 05:30.520
in class?

05:30.800 --> 05:31.640
You didn't cheat on the physics exam.

05:31.640 --> 05:32.700
Why did you admit it

05:32.880 --> 05:34.200
and say you copied mine?

05:34.200 --> 05:35.130
What do you mean?

05:35.320 --> 05:36.380
Why did you do that?

05:36.440 --> 05:38.920
Alright. Let's see how you explain it.

05:39.680 --> 05:41.880
If I'm wrong, you tell me.

05:49.720 --> 05:50.680
Jingu, what a coincidence.

05:50.680 --> 05:52.080
I was just about to knock.

05:52.840 --> 05:54.400
Are you going out?

05:54.800 --> 05:55.560
Didn't we agree

05:55.560 --> 05:56.840
you'd tutor me today?

05:57.480 --> 05:58.120
Xinrui.

05:58.600 --> 05:59.960
Sorry, I forgot.

06:00.480 --> 06:02.940
How about I tutor you when I get back tonight?

06:03.160 --> 06:05.290
Do you have something important to do?

06:06.480 --> 06:07.600
Do you need my help?

06:07.800 --> 06:08.600
No, thanks.

06:08.800 --> 06:10.040
You should go back and rest first.

06:10.040 --> 06:12.100
I'll call you when I get back tonight.

06:12.280 --> 06:13.320
Okay.

06:13.400 --> 06:15.320
Then I'll wait for your call.

06:15.640 --> 06:17.720
Okay, I'll get going. Bye.

06:19.400 --> 06:21.260
Remember to close the door for me.

06:31.160 --> 06:31.880
Tutoring?

06:32.520 --> 06:33.240
Well,

06:34.360 --> 06:36.090
you don't mind if I join, do you?

06:37.360 --> 06:38.840
Why are you so late?

06:38.960 --> 06:40.490
I've been waiting for ages.

06:41.000 --> 06:43.080
I just went to the restroom.

06:44.640 --> 06:45.200
Here.

06:45.640 --> 06:46.520
Move over a bit.

06:46.880 --> 06:49.480
My grades are poor. I need to be closer to Jingu.

06:59.000 --> 06:59.720
Go ahead.

07:04.000 --> 07:06.730
A skydiver is doing a low-altitude performance.

07:06.760 --> 07:09.080
When the plane is 224 meters above the ground,

07:09.080 --> 07:10.360
flying horizontally,

07:10.400 --> 07:12.400
the skydiver leaves the plane

07:12.440 --> 07:15.040
and free falls in the vertical direction.

07:16.480 --> 07:18.240
Come on, have some fruit.

07:21.760 --> 07:24.320
Do you both like strawberries?

07:24.480 --> 07:25.760
I'll go get some more.

07:32.440 --> 07:33.320
Let me tell you.

07:33.640 --> 07:35.280
Even though Yuanbao forgave you,

07:35.280 --> 07:36.520
I haven't.

07:36.880 --> 07:38.720
If you hadn't stood her up,

07:39.040 --> 07:40.800
her performance wouldn't have been placed last,

07:40.800 --> 07:42.930
and her eye wouldn't have gotten hurt.

07:43.159 --> 07:44.820
You have a guilty conscience.

07:45.040 --> 07:46.320
You were afraid I'd go to your house

07:46.320 --> 07:48.050
and expose your big lie, right?

07:48.880 --> 07:50.409
What are you talking about?

08:02.960 --> 08:04.020
What are you doing?

08:06.120 --> 08:07.380
Are you going to fight?

08:15.720 --> 08:17.200
Walk Jingu downstairs properly

08:17.200 --> 08:18.560
and let him take the fruit back.

08:18.560 --> 08:19.360
Hear me?

08:22.960 --> 08:25.480
Jingu, thanks for your hard work today.

08:25.720 --> 08:27.760
Come over often to tutor them.

08:28.200 --> 08:29.800
You two young men

08:30.120 --> 08:32.120
should be good friends, okay?

08:32.440 --> 08:34.200
Don't worry, Auntie. We will.

08:35.200 --> 08:36.240
Go on.

08:36.720 --> 08:39.440
Jingu, text me when you get home.

08:40.080 --> 08:40.809
Don't worry.

08:40.919 --> 08:41.760
Bye, Auntie.

08:59.400 --> 09:00.280
Make up.

09:06.160 --> 09:07.360
Stop messing around.

09:07.400 --> 09:08.240
Go up quickly.

09:26.840 --> 09:27.500
Apologize.

09:29.080 --> 09:30.000
I'm sorry.

09:30.400 --> 09:31.200
And what else?

09:34.160 --> 09:35.440
Love you.

09:37.160 --> 09:37.880
Sing.

09:41.400 --> 09:45.200
Because we are family.

09:57.560 --> 09:58.490
Where did you go?

09:58.800 --> 10:00.400
Why did you come back so late?

10:02.720 --> 10:04.650
Since the last drama performance,

10:05.320 --> 10:07.120
you've been giving me the cold shoulder for days.

10:07.120 --> 10:08.200
If Xinrui hadn't

10:08.200 --> 10:10.130
been putting in a good word for you,

10:10.240 --> 10:12.160
would you have ignored me for the rest of your life?

10:12.160 --> 10:13.680
Do you know that Xinrui

10:13.720 --> 10:15.720
has been waiting for you at home all day today?

10:15.720 --> 10:16.600
Didn't you promise

10:16.600 --> 10:17.880
to tutor her?

10:18.920 --> 10:20.920
You two are childhood sweethearts.

10:21.120 --> 10:23.240
Xinrui is a British citizen now,

10:23.440 --> 10:25.170
and just came back from abroad.

10:25.280 --> 10:27.080
You need to take good care of her.

10:27.520 --> 10:30.050
When you have time, you should tutor her well.

10:30.080 --> 10:32.040
Only a good girl like Xinrui

10:32.160 --> 10:33.560
and a family like hers

10:33.680 --> 10:35.480
can truly help you in the future.

10:36.880 --> 10:37.760
Did you hear me?

10:38.080 --> 10:39.740
Did you hear me talking to you?

10:42.520 --> 10:43.840
Don't be mad.

10:46.760 --> 10:47.360
Jingu,

10:48.040 --> 10:50.640
what's with this medical insurance contract?

10:52.680 --> 10:54.680
I asked a classmate's parent for it.

10:54.760 --> 10:56.120
I think you should buy it.

10:56.120 --> 10:57.380
A classmate's parent?

10:57.840 --> 10:59.640
Is it the mother of that Yuanbao?

10:59.720 --> 11:00.400
Yes.

11:00.920 --> 11:02.640
What kind of family is this?

11:02.960 --> 11:04.680
They just want you to spend money.

11:04.680 --> 11:06.640
They probably want you to buy a house.

11:06.640 --> 11:08.440
Medical insurance is all the same.

11:08.440 --> 11:09.640
It's the same wherever you buy it.

11:09.640 --> 11:10.920
How is it the same?

11:11.760 --> 11:14.640
If you buy it, you should buy it from someone with high quality, high education,

11:14.640 --> 11:16.080
and high income.

11:16.280 --> 11:17.810
That way, it's guaranteed.

11:21.640 --> 11:23.560
I'm tired. I'm going back to rest.

11:25.560 --> 11:26.320
Jingu.

11:29.800 --> 11:30.720
Don't be mad.

11:47.680 --> 11:49.080
Xiong Yuanbao, come on!

11:58.440 --> 11:59.700
Come, let's go inside.

12:01.040 --> 12:02.570
Why don't you ride the bike?

12:03.920 --> 12:05.760
You're already this dizzy walking.

12:05.760 --> 12:07.880
It would be worse on the back of a bike.

12:08.240 --> 12:09.570
Let's take a taxi later.

12:10.120 --> 12:10.920
A taxi?

12:11.320 --> 12:13.600
No, it's too expensive.

12:13.680 --> 12:14.880
I have to save money.

12:16.280 --> 12:17.920
What for?

12:18.080 --> 12:19.040
Of course,

12:21.840 --> 12:24.720
to see Jay Chou's concert.

12:27.200 --> 12:28.280
In that case,

12:28.600 --> 12:30.560
you can't be late for school tomorrow.

12:30.560 --> 12:32.800
Don't show up just in time for lunch.

12:36.320 --> 12:37.160
No, stop.

12:37.200 --> 12:38.800
I'm a little dizzy right now.

12:39.760 --> 12:40.600
Come on.

12:42.560 --> 12:43.240
Sit here.

12:48.680 --> 12:49.560
Come, stand up.

12:50.760 --> 12:51.320
Stand up.

12:52.480 --> 12:53.360
Step up here.

12:58.360 --> 12:59.000
What?

12:59.280 --> 13:00.200
I'll carry you on my back.

13:00.200 --> 13:01.200
Why?

13:01.360 --> 13:03.000
I'm not lame or blind.

13:03.720 --> 13:05.520
Just be good and listen to me.

13:10.520 --> 13:11.080
Yuanbao.

13:12.600 --> 13:13.280
What is it?

13:16.200 --> 13:19.000
Why did you call me and say nothing?

13:20.840 --> 13:21.600
Nothing.

13:23.880 --> 13:25.520
So mysterious.

13:31.160 --> 13:32.200
Put me down.

13:37.600 --> 13:38.320
Yuanbao.

13:38.640 --> 13:39.400
Yuanbao.

13:41.040 --> 13:42.040
Why are you here?

13:42.360 --> 13:43.690
Do your eyes still hurt?

13:44.160 --> 13:44.840
I'm fine.

13:44.840 --> 13:46.920
Didn't I text you about it?

13:47.600 --> 13:48.560
Let me help you.

13:53.080 --> 13:54.810
I didn't see it with my own eyes.

13:54.960 --> 13:56.240
I was so worried.

13:58.760 --> 14:00.440
Pirates of the Caribbean!

14:00.520 --> 14:01.480
Wow, big shot.

14:01.560 --> 14:03.360
You even brought a bodyguard.

14:03.640 --> 14:05.170
What are you talking about?

14:05.680 --> 14:07.320
Yuanbao, with your eyes painted like this,

14:07.320 --> 14:08.520
can you even see?

14:08.760 --> 14:09.960
You look a bit like...

14:10.400 --> 14:11.920
Zhu, zhu, zhu...

14:11.960 --> 14:12.920
Zhu what?

14:13.800 --> 14:15.720
Angelina Jolie.

14:15.840 --> 14:16.900
Right, that Jolie.

14:18.640 --> 14:20.440
Remember to take your medicine.

14:26.480 --> 14:27.120
Go back.

14:30.840 --> 14:31.680
Yuanbao is back.

14:31.680 --> 14:32.560
When did you get back?

14:32.560 --> 14:32.960
Just now.

14:32.960 --> 14:33.560
Really?

14:35.680 --> 14:36.610
Yuanbao is back.

14:36.920 --> 14:38.920
Let's applaud and welcome her back.

14:45.960 --> 14:47.920
Class, Yuanbao

14:48.040 --> 14:49.520
fought for the honor of our class

14:49.520 --> 14:50.650
in this competition

14:50.680 --> 14:51.680
and was accidentally injured.

14:51.680 --> 14:53.360
Good thing it only hurt the eyelid.

14:53.360 --> 14:54.200
So I am here

14:54.240 --> 14:55.320
to remind everyone that

14:55.320 --> 14:56.640
during the three years of high school,

14:56.640 --> 14:58.640
health and safety are the most important.

14:58.640 --> 14:59.200
I hope everyone

14:59.200 --> 15:00.600
in your daily lives

15:00.760 --> 15:01.960
will pay attention to safety.

15:01.960 --> 15:02.820
Did you hear me?

15:03.040 --> 15:04.240
Yes.

15:04.680 --> 15:06.840
There's something I must say.

15:07.520 --> 15:08.450
Unfortunately,

15:08.640 --> 15:10.000
our class's performance

15:10.000 --> 15:12.130
wasn't selected in this competition.

15:13.440 --> 15:14.280
However,

15:14.520 --> 15:15.400
an enthusiastic viewer

15:15.400 --> 15:16.930
uploaded our video online,

15:17.000 --> 15:19.860
and the views have already exceeded three million.

15:20.080 --> 15:21.400
Many enthusiastic viewers

15:21.400 --> 15:23.530
say you have a great talent for acting,

15:23.640 --> 15:26.100
and that you performed exceptionally well.

15:26.120 --> 15:26.800
Okay.

15:30.680 --> 15:32.140
Through this experience,

15:32.280 --> 15:33.740
I want to tell everyone...

15:34.080 --> 15:34.840
Sometimes,

15:34.880 --> 15:36.320
winning or losing isn't that important.

15:36.320 --> 15:38.920
As long as you participate, you will gain something.

15:38.920 --> 15:41.360
Don't be overly joyful over gains or sad over losses.

15:41.360 --> 15:43.520
Success is just a matter of time, okay?

15:43.760 --> 15:45.360
Okay.

15:48.440 --> 15:49.160
Okay, then.

15:49.240 --> 15:51.240
Study by yourselves for this class.

15:57.000 --> 15:58.000
Is it ugly?

15:58.280 --> 15:59.940
You mean the eye on your gauze?

16:00.760 --> 16:01.960
Compared to your eye,

16:02.320 --> 16:04.320
it's really not that good-looking.

16:04.720 --> 16:05.600
Actually,

16:05.880 --> 16:07.960
you really didn't have to rush to class.

16:07.960 --> 16:10.400
I'll tutor you on the weekend anyway.

16:11.640 --> 16:13.120
It's so boring at home.

16:13.520 --> 16:14.600
I'd rather come to school.

16:14.600 --> 16:16.600
It's more fun to stay with everyone.

16:22.360 --> 16:23.280
How is it?

16:34.320 --> 16:36.120
Doctor, what's wrong?

16:36.800 --> 16:38.520
Is my face ruined?

16:38.880 --> 16:40.760
Am I ugly now?

16:41.040 --> 16:42.760
Her skin is healing very well,

16:43.000 --> 16:44.320
leaving no scars.

16:44.400 --> 16:45.680
It's really a blessing.

16:45.680 --> 16:48.010
But you must be more careful in the future.

16:48.160 --> 16:49.320
Thank you, Doctor.

16:49.560 --> 16:51.200
Thank you, doctor. Thanks for your hard work.

16:51.200 --> 16:51.840
You're welcome.

16:51.840 --> 16:53.680
Everything is fine. You can go back.

16:53.680 --> 16:54.480
Okay.

16:55.040 --> 16:56.120
Look at you.

16:56.200 --> 16:57.400
It was so dangerous this time.

16:57.400 --> 16:58.560
You were lucky.

16:58.640 --> 17:00.280
We were worried to death.

17:00.680 --> 17:01.360
Yeah.

17:01.800 --> 17:03.000
From now on, you and Qingyun

17:03.000 --> 17:04.640
should focus on your studies.

17:04.640 --> 17:06.640
Don't participate in other activities.

17:06.640 --> 17:08.440
The final exams are coming soon.

17:09.079 --> 17:10.880
Let Meng Jingu tutor you again.

17:12.160 --> 17:13.040
Got it.

17:18.960 --> 17:21.599
Goodbye, teacher.

17:22.680 --> 17:24.680
Ruirui, let's go get the workbooks.

17:26.880 --> 17:27.520
Yuanbao.

17:27.599 --> 17:28.760
Do you want to go for a walk?

17:28.760 --> 17:30.160
We can chat along the way.

17:30.760 --> 17:31.520
Sure.

17:31.800 --> 17:32.480
Let's go.

17:34.880 --> 17:36.140
What's wrong, Xinrui?

17:37.400 --> 17:39.280
I was in a hurry to notify you at the theater that day.

17:39.280 --> 17:40.810
I accidentally fell again.

17:41.080 --> 17:43.040
Then let me go with you to the infirmary.

17:43.040 --> 17:43.640
It's fine.

17:43.880 --> 17:46.400
It's inconvenient for you with your injured eye.

17:46.400 --> 17:47.200
Jingu.

17:47.520 --> 17:49.450
Can you go to the infirmary with me?

17:51.000 --> 17:51.760
Yuanbao.

17:51.960 --> 17:53.560
I'll go to the infirmary with Xinrui.

17:53.560 --> 17:55.960
Ask for leave for us when the teacher comes.

18:02.560 --> 18:04.720
Then we'll talk when we get back.

18:05.520 --> 18:06.240
Okay.

18:06.560 --> 18:07.690
We're leaving then.

18:07.720 --> 18:08.520
Okay.

18:17.920 --> 18:18.680
Xinrui,

18:19.080 --> 18:21.080
is your back injury feeling better?

18:21.360 --> 18:22.090
Much better.

18:22.680 --> 18:24.410
Old injuries take time to heal.

18:25.360 --> 18:26.640
Your eye is better too.

18:26.800 --> 18:28.930
It's great that it didn't leave a scar.

18:29.440 --> 18:30.880
Yeah, I was really lucky.

18:31.920 --> 18:33.760
If you need any help in the future,

18:33.760 --> 18:34.690
just let me know.

18:35.080 --> 18:36.440
It's fine. I have Jingu.

18:36.560 --> 18:37.760
He can take care of me.

18:38.800 --> 18:39.560
Okay.

18:40.520 --> 18:41.120
By the way,

18:41.680 --> 18:43.160
actually, the day you just came back,

18:43.160 --> 18:44.360
I wanted to tell you.

18:44.840 --> 18:46.700
But my back injury acted up again,

18:46.800 --> 18:48.460
so I didn't have time to say it.

18:48.520 --> 18:49.440
What is it?

18:50.440 --> 18:51.280
Well,

18:51.560 --> 18:54.090
I don't want you to misunderstand Meng Jingu.

18:54.280 --> 18:57.800
Actually, he couldn't go to the live performance that day

18:58.440 --> 18:59.840
because he had no choice.

19:00.880 --> 19:02.520
Jingu was locked up that day.

19:04.040 --> 19:05.360
Locked up?

19:07.200 --> 19:08.520
Uncle Meng doesn't like it

19:08.520 --> 19:10.680
when he participates in activities unrelated to his studies,

19:10.680 --> 19:12.120
so he is very strict with him.

19:12.120 --> 19:14.600
So I hope you won't misunderstand him

19:15.280 --> 19:16.800
or blame him. Okay?

19:18.400 --> 19:21.040
Although I knew he had his difficulties,

19:21.560 --> 19:22.420
I didn't expect

19:22.480 --> 19:24.440
that something like this would happen that day.

19:24.440 --> 19:27.320
Xinrui, thank you for telling me this.

19:28.360 --> 19:29.080
No problem.

19:29.880 --> 19:31.340
Jingu is the kind of person

19:31.360 --> 19:33.080
who really values his friends.

19:33.080 --> 19:34.540
He mentions you to me a lot.

19:34.680 --> 19:36.680
He says you're straightforward, loyal,

19:36.680 --> 19:37.940
and a good buddy of his.

19:37.960 --> 19:41.220
So he doesn't want any misunderstandings between you two.

19:41.400 --> 19:42.760
A good buddy.

19:46.040 --> 19:47.240
He's just like that.

19:47.840 --> 19:49.960
Ever since we were kids, whenever he's misunderstood,

19:49.960 --> 19:51.420
he never defends himself.

19:52.080 --> 19:53.920
So I have to speak up for Jingu.

19:54.680 --> 19:58.680
Did Meng Jingu ask you to tell me this?

19:59.360 --> 20:00.280
No, he didn't.

20:01.200 --> 20:03.600
But whenever this happened in the past,

20:03.880 --> 20:06.140
I was always the one to sort it out for him.

20:06.240 --> 20:09.100
I've lost count of how many times since we were kids.

20:09.560 --> 20:10.560
I'm used to it.

20:11.280 --> 20:14.080
I wonder how many people

20:15.360 --> 20:18.020
Jingu has offended during the year I was abroad.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.240
So, Yuanbao,

20:22.560 --> 20:24.880
you're not mad at Jingu anymore, right?

20:25.760 --> 20:26.640
Of course not.

20:28.320 --> 20:29.720
That puts my mind at ease.

20:30.240 --> 20:30.960
Yuanbao.

20:31.160 --> 20:32.880
If he does anything wrong again in the future,

20:32.880 --> 20:33.640
just tell me.

20:33.760 --> 20:35.960
I'll teach Jingu a lesson for you, okay?

20:37.040 --> 20:37.680
Okay.

20:39.200 --> 20:41.560
Xinrui, is there anything else?

20:41.920 --> 20:44.120
If not, I'll head back first.

20:44.840 --> 20:45.640
Nothing else.

20:45.720 --> 20:47.050
Let's go back together.

20:52.720 --> 20:54.980
What's wrong? Does your back hurt again?

20:55.680 --> 20:56.540
Let me help you.

20:58.080 --> 20:59.280
Thank you, Yuanbao.

20:59.640 --> 21:00.640
You're so loyal.

21:00.800 --> 21:03.000
No wonder boys like being your bros.

21:04.640 --> 21:05.520
Then let's

21:05.800 --> 21:06.960
be good sisters.

21:09.160 --> 21:10.040
Sure.

21:12.360 --> 21:12.960
Slow down.

21:26.680 --> 21:29.920
Deskmate, Xinrui came to me today

21:30.000 --> 21:32.800
and told me what happened on the day of the competition.

21:32.800 --> 21:35.040
I didn't expect things to be like that.

21:35.320 --> 21:37.200
I was even mad at you then.

21:37.560 --> 21:38.800
I'm really sorry.

21:43.640 --> 21:44.360
Yuanbao.

21:44.720 --> 21:46.380
Thank you for understanding.

21:46.400 --> 21:48.860
I've never been good at opening up to others,

21:48.880 --> 21:51.120
nor am I used to talking about family matters.

21:51.120 --> 21:52.080
So,

21:52.280 --> 21:54.640
failing to explain things clearly to you in time

21:54.640 --> 21:55.800
was my fault.

21:57.720 --> 21:59.080
Everyone has things

21:59.120 --> 22:01.240
they don't want to confide in others.

22:01.680 --> 22:02.720
I understand.

22:03.440 --> 22:06.500
But keeping things bottled up for too long gets tiring.

22:07.720 --> 22:09.240
Thank you for understanding.

22:09.240 --> 22:12.640
Can I talk to you when I have something on my mind in the future?

22:17.520 --> 22:19.480
Sure. We can help each other.

22:19.560 --> 22:22.200
Then don't find me annoying later.

22:24.200 --> 22:25.280
Okay.

22:29.880 --> 22:31.840
I wonder what Gu Xinrui

22:31.920 --> 22:33.720
wanted to talk to me about today.

22:34.080 --> 22:36.160
It's always good to text back.

22:47.680 --> 22:49.610
I can't believe I ran into you here.

22:50.000 --> 22:51.200
What a rare occasion.

22:51.760 --> 22:53.320
It's a small world.

22:54.480 --> 22:55.340
Xiong Yuanbao.

22:56.320 --> 22:57.960
I'm just really curious.

22:58.120 --> 22:58.960
Tell me,

22:59.320 --> 23:02.200
you seem to study hard every day,

23:03.320 --> 23:05.720
so why are your test scores always the same?

23:06.440 --> 23:08.880
And you just goof around every day.

23:09.240 --> 23:10.920
Aren't you worried?

23:13.840 --> 23:16.170
You wouldn't understand a fairy's world.

23:16.320 --> 23:17.640
A fairy's world?

23:19.000 --> 23:21.600
Did this fairy land face-first?

23:22.560 --> 23:24.490
Xiong Yuanbao, as your classmate,

23:24.520 --> 23:26.080
let me give you a piece of advice.

23:26.080 --> 23:28.080
If you want to be on Meng Jingu's level,

23:28.080 --> 23:29.400
you have to study hard.

23:29.800 --> 23:32.080
Don't act like that naive Tong Ruirui all day,

23:32.080 --> 23:34.040
doing nothing but reading romance novels.

23:34.040 --> 23:37.200
Can reading those get you a college acceptance letter?

23:38.320 --> 23:40.520
Can they win you the heart of your crush?

23:40.960 --> 23:42.760
Idol dramas and romance novels

23:43.400 --> 23:45.600
are just meant to trick ignorant girls.

23:46.320 --> 23:47.320
What is reality?

23:48.120 --> 23:50.050
A strong alliance between equals,

23:50.360 --> 23:52.520
like Gu Xinrui and Meng Jingu.

23:53.400 --> 23:54.460
Do you understand?

23:56.680 --> 23:58.280
Just mind your own business.

23:58.400 --> 24:00.680
You're taking my good intentions for ill will.

24:00.680 --> 24:02.140
Whatever, suit yourself.

24:07.000 --> 24:07.680
Look at you.

24:08.440 --> 24:09.440
You have no shame.

24:12.840 --> 24:13.900
What are you doing?

24:14.200 --> 24:16.200
As your classmate, I'm kindly reminding you,

24:16.200 --> 24:17.530
you've got your period.

24:22.040 --> 24:23.900
Let me go to the restroom with you.

24:32.640 --> 24:33.400
Thanks.

24:37.240 --> 24:38.170
What did you say?

24:39.920 --> 24:40.880
I said,

24:42.440 --> 24:44.880
thank you for buying this for me

24:45.520 --> 24:47.200
and lending me your jacket.

24:50.280 --> 24:52.160
Now that you've seen me make a fool of myself,

24:52.160 --> 24:54.360
you must be feeling pretty smug, right?

24:55.280 --> 24:58.000
It's the first time I've heard you say thank you.

24:58.800 --> 25:00.130
I just found it strange.

25:06.680 --> 25:07.360
Qiao Yan,

25:08.040 --> 25:11.040
why are you always like a hedgehog towards me?

25:12.440 --> 25:13.840
I just have it out for you.

25:14.600 --> 25:17.530
And don't think just because you helped me this time,

25:17.800 --> 25:20.130
I won't hold grudges against you anymore.

25:22.640 --> 25:23.320
Qiao Yan,

25:25.760 --> 25:28.400
I think I know why.

25:29.360 --> 25:30.720
I'll tell you today.

25:31.200 --> 25:34.000
Everything I saw on the street that day,

25:34.880 --> 25:36.840
I haven't told anyone.

25:44.960 --> 25:45.760
I know.

25:48.680 --> 25:49.440
Thank you.

25:51.480 --> 25:52.120
By the way,

25:53.000 --> 25:53.800
in the future,

25:54.400 --> 25:55.460
with your studies,

25:56.160 --> 25:57.720
if you have any problems,

25:59.200 --> 26:00.200
you can come to me.

26:01.440 --> 26:02.440
I'll be going now.

26:18.840 --> 26:20.240
Dad, be careful.

26:21.240 --> 26:22.320
Let me go.

26:23.080 --> 26:24.840
Why aren't you going home to do your homework?

26:24.840 --> 26:26.240
Why are you following me?

26:26.360 --> 26:27.800
Dad, hurry up and leave.

26:29.760 --> 26:31.090
If you don't study hard,

26:31.600 --> 26:34.000
do you want to end up like me today?

26:34.680 --> 26:35.480
Dad, let's go home.

26:35.480 --> 26:36.160
Get up.

26:36.400 --> 26:37.880
Did you hear me?

26:38.000 --> 26:39.040
Get lost.

26:39.680 --> 26:41.320
Why did you hit my classmate?

26:44.040 --> 26:45.120
He is my dad.

27:04.280 --> 27:05.160
I'm sorry.

27:05.640 --> 27:08.320
The doctor said I can't move around too much with my back injury,

27:08.320 --> 27:11.560
so I have to stay in the classroom for lunch.

27:11.960 --> 27:14.000
And it makes you have to stay here with me.

27:14.000 --> 27:14.800
It's fine.

27:16.200 --> 27:16.960
I know

27:17.200 --> 27:19.880
you hate it the most when Uncle Meng orders you around.

27:19.880 --> 27:23.010
This time when he told you to eat with me in the classroom,

27:23.240 --> 27:25.440
he probably used a commanding tone again.

27:25.440 --> 27:26.570
He's just like that.

27:28.760 --> 27:31.760
It was my mom who told the doctor not to let me move much.

27:31.800 --> 27:32.840
I think she probably

27:32.840 --> 27:34.680
when she was talking to Aunt Meng,

27:34.680 --> 27:36.140
mentioned it by accident.

27:37.080 --> 27:37.840
Let's eat.

27:38.560 --> 27:41.200
Even if my dad didn't say it, I'd still take care of you.

27:41.200 --> 27:43.330
We're basically siblings, after all.

27:49.160 --> 27:52.290
I specially asked our maid to make your favorite dishes.

27:52.600 --> 27:54.200
Didn't you used to say all the time

27:54.200 --> 27:55.600
that she was a great cook?

27:55.640 --> 27:56.800
During the years I was abroad,

27:56.800 --> 27:58.120
you didn't get to eat her cooking.

27:58.120 --> 27:58.800
Try it.

27:59.440 --> 27:59.920
Okay.

28:00.040 --> 28:02.520
This is really good.

28:06.080 --> 28:08.560
Are you still mad at me

28:08.640 --> 28:11.840
for leaving early to go abroad by myself?

28:12.240 --> 28:13.040
No.

28:14.280 --> 28:15.400
I know

28:15.680 --> 28:18.080
that for the sake of dance,

28:18.160 --> 28:19.690
I chose to leave you behind.

28:20.200 --> 28:22.560
Later, I injured my back abroad

28:22.800 --> 28:23.960
and came running back to you.

28:23.960 --> 28:25.240
I was wrong.

28:26.440 --> 28:27.520
But Jingu,

28:29.400 --> 28:31.440
you know how much effort and dedication

28:31.440 --> 28:33.280
I put into dancing.

28:34.760 --> 28:36.040
Now that dance is gone,

28:37.360 --> 28:38.680
I don't want my best friend

28:38.680 --> 28:40.080
to drift away from me too.

28:41.880 --> 28:42.680
Okay?

28:47.000 --> 28:48.240
I'm not mad at you.

28:48.720 --> 28:49.720
I can understand.

28:51.000 --> 28:52.060
It's just, Xinrui,

28:52.800 --> 28:53.800
we've grown up.

28:54.640 --> 28:56.280
We can't be like when we were kids

28:56.280 --> 28:57.800
and stick together all day.

28:57.800 --> 28:59.320
We both have our own lives.

29:00.000 --> 29:02.840
Drifting apart doesn't mean we're not close.

29:03.560 --> 29:04.360
It's just that

29:05.120 --> 29:07.180
we should both try to be independent.

29:09.480 --> 29:12.340
Take your time eating. I'm going to grab a document.

29:39.040 --> 29:39.760
Ruirui.

29:40.280 --> 29:41.740
Weren't you with Yuanbao?

29:41.840 --> 29:42.570
Where is she?

29:43.000 --> 29:44.600
Yuanbao went to the library.

29:44.640 --> 29:46.440
So I came to buy some food myself.

29:46.800 --> 29:48.800
She rarely goes to the library all year.

29:48.800 --> 29:50.260
Why the sudden whim today?

29:50.680 --> 29:51.560
She said...

29:52.040 --> 29:54.520
Finals are coming. She needs to cram.

29:56.920 --> 29:57.800
What is this?

29:59.640 --> 30:01.560
I don't think this big eater ate well at noon.

30:01.560 --> 30:02.960
So I bought her some feed.

30:03.040 --> 30:04.080
I'll take it to her now.

30:04.080 --> 30:05.740
Anyway, I'm going to find her.

30:10.720 --> 30:13.680
It's so great to have a brother like Qingyun.

30:48.560 --> 30:50.290
Aren't you going to grab a book?

30:56.000 --> 30:59.080
When did you get here? You scared me.

31:00.040 --> 31:01.100
I just got here too.

31:01.360 --> 31:02.760
What book did you choose?

31:05.040 --> 31:05.720
This one.

31:05.720 --> 31:06.600
Cyclic learning, memorize until you know it, guaranteed effect!

31:06.600 --> 31:07.730
I've read this book.

31:08.080 --> 31:11.480
The content is a bit too general, so it's not very suitable for you.

31:11.480 --> 31:12.340
How about this?

31:12.720 --> 31:15.250
Later, based on your ability and foundation,

31:15.480 --> 31:17.000
I'll organize a specific set of

31:17.000 --> 31:18.460
physics concepts for you.

31:18.720 --> 31:20.280
It will be more targeted

31:20.400 --> 31:21.440
and more suitable for you.

31:21.440 --> 31:22.200
Really?

31:22.360 --> 31:23.040
Of course.

31:24.440 --> 31:25.600
You read this first.

31:25.880 --> 31:28.120
I'll go pick out a few other materials for you.

31:28.120 --> 31:28.980
As for this one,

31:30.160 --> 31:31.020
just forget it.

31:54.840 --> 31:56.280
Did Mutou buy this?

31:56.600 --> 31:58.040
Why didn't he say anything?
